A collection of independent financial calculators built with React, TypeScript, and Vite. Each calculator can be compiled to a single, self-contained HTML file for easy distribution and embedding.\
\
## Current Calculators\
\
### Retirement Calculator \
**URL:** `/src/retirement.html`  \
**Build Output:** `dist/retirement.html`\
\
A comprehensive retirement planning calculator that helps users determine if they're on track to meet their retirement goals.\
\
**Features:**\
- Natural language form input for better user experience\
- Real-time retirement projections with compound interest calculations\
- Interactive chart showing savings progression over time\
- Clear guidance on whether user is on track or needs to save more\
- Calculates additional monthly savings needed if behind on goals\
\
**Form Inputs:**\
- Current age and planned retirement age\
- Annual income and current annual savings\
- Current retirement savings balance\
- Expected retirement income needs (% of current income)\
- Expected annual investment return\
\
