## Architecture\
\
Each calculator is completely independent and follows these principles:\
- **KISS (Keep It Simple, Stupid)** - Clean, minimal code\
- **Component-based** - Reusable React components\
- **Two-step UX** - Clean input form \uc0\u8594  Results display\
- **Natural language forms** - Embedded inputs in conversational text\
- **Single file distribution** - Each calculator compiles to one HTML file\
- **Clean \cf2 \cb5 \strokec6 design\cf2 \cb3 \strokec4 ** - Following Airbnb/Coinbase \cf2 \cb5 \strokec6 design\cf2 \cb3 \strokec4  principles\
