## Adding New Calculators\
\
1. Create a new directory under `src/` (e.g., `src/mortgage/`)\
2. Add HTML entry point (e.g., `src/mortgage.html`)\
3. Create calculator component with natural language form\
4. Update `vite.config.ts` to include new entry point\
5. Follow the established patterns for styling and UX\
